---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Disclaimer | Trucker Copilot"
  description="Important disclosures about financing, credit information, and third-party data presented through Trucker Copilot and the FactorEvo network."
>
  <section class="hero" style="padding-bottom:1.5rem;">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
      <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
      <p class="article-meta">Last updated: July 21, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="padding-top:0.5rem;">
    <div class="container container--narrow prose">
      <h2>No financing guarantee</h2>
      <p>
        Trucker Copilot is not a lender, factoring company, broker of financial products, or
        financial advisor. Trucker Copilot connects carriers and transaction information with
        participating specialty finance companies through the FactorEvo network. Any financing
        agreement is entered into directly between the carrier and the selected finance company.
        Approval, funding, rates, fees, advance amounts, reserves, recourse structure, timing, and
        all other terms are determined solely by that provider and remain subject to its
        eligibility, verification, and underwriting requirements. Trucker Copilot does not guarantee
        approval, funding, or funding speed.
      </p>

      <h2>Credit and third-party information</h2>
      <p>
        Broker, shipper, and debtor credit information, FMCSA and operating authority data, fuel
        prices, routes, and load information displayed in the Services come from third-party
        sources and connected data services. This information is provided for general reference
        only, may be incomplete, delayed, or inaccurate, and is not a recommendation to accept or
        reject any load, counterparty, or business relationship. You are responsible for your own
        operating and business decisions.
      </p>

      <h2>Not legal, tax, or financial advice</h2>
      <p>
        Content on this website, including resource articles, is provided for general informational
        purposes only and does not constitute legal, tax, accounting, or financial advice. Consult
        your own advisors before making decisions that affect your business.
      </p>

      <h2>Feature availability</h2>
      <p>
        Some features described on this website may be provider-dependent, integration-dependent,
        in limited release, or planned. Availability can vary by carrier, finance company,
        platform, and region.
      </p>

      <h2>Ecosystem</h2>
      <p>
        Trucker Copilot is part of the FactorEvo Group Holdings ecosystem. The mobile platform is
        being developed in strategic partnership with CargoNerd. References to FactorEvo describe
        the financial infrastructure used by participating finance companies and do not make
        Trucker Copilot a party to any financing agreement.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
